### {{projectNamePascal}} Deployment Guideline

## Setup AWS configuration profile
- Create a deployment user in IAM: `simplify-user`
- Setup IAM Role policy using: `deployment-policy.json`
- Configure your machine `aws configure --profile simplify-eu`

*** Install deployment project dependancies ***
`npm install`

*** Create stack resources and default function configurations ***
`npm run stack-deploy`

*** Push source code of every functions defined in .env and function-input.json ***
`npm run push-code`

*** Run unit tests and local express server for debugging ***
`cd {{projectName}} && npm install`
`npm run test-units`
`npm start`

*** Run test remote APIs against {{projectNamePascal}} API Gateway ***
`npm run test-apis`

*** Push configuration of every functions defined in .env and function-input.json ***
`npm run push-update`

*** Cleanup stack resources and destroy every function's dependancies (including layers) ***
`npm run stack-destroy`

